Package: crisstats
Title: University Publication Productivity Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mohammed", "Saqr", , "mohammed.saqr@uef.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for analyzing university publication productivity
    from CRIS (Current Research Information System) data exports. Features
    one-stop data preparation with automatic organizational hierarchy mapping,
    comprehensive report generation, flexible comparison functions with wildcard
    pattern matching, and automatic visualization. Includes author productivity
    analysis with multiple fractional counting methods, publication statistics,
    and unit-level analysis. Designed for JUFO-ranked publications from Finnish
    universities.
